        public boolean hasPathTo(java.lang.String countryId,
                         java.lang.String ownerId,
                         java.util.HashSet<java.lang.String> visited)
        Depth-first recursive search to determine if there's a linked path owned by same player to the destination Country with countryId
        Parameters:
        countryId - destination countryId
        ownerId - playerId who is suppoed to own the path
        visited - HashSet of visited id of Countries during the recursive call
        Returns:
        false if no such path is found, true if yes
